high_descs: Walk to the fridge, then walk right to the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn right, then turn right again and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the left.
Pick up the pot and knife from the stove.
Turn around and face the table.
Set the pot and knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and pot on the table.

high_descs: Walk across the room and stand in front of the sink.
Pick up the sharp knife next to the butter knife.
Turn right and stand in front of the stove.
Place the knife in the pan that's on the back left burner on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn around and stand in front of the counter with the coffee maker on the left.
Place the pan on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To get a pan to slice tomatoes.

high_descs: Go to the sink on the right.
Pick up the knife in front of the sink.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the left.
Pick up the pot with the knife in it.
Turn around and go to the table.
Put the pot with the knife in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a pot on the table.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Move to the stove to your right.
Place the knife inside the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the knife in it.
Move to the the table to the right of you.
Place the pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife inside on the table in front of the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and begin walking to the fridge, hang a right and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle that is on the counter in front of the rightmost sink.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the oven.
Place the large metal knife point down into the metal pot that is on the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the large metal pot with the knife in it off of the stove.
Turn left and begin walking forward, then turn left again and walk over to the white table with the coffee machine on it.
Place the metal pot with the knife in it onto the white table to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a large metal pot with a knife in it on a white table.

high_descs: turn right and walk towards sinks, stop in front of sinks
pick up sharp knife with gold handle
turn right and walk straight to the stove, turn left and face stove
put knife into left container on stove top
pick up left container on stove top
turn left and walk straight, at the fridge, turn left and continue walking, stop in front of white table  with tomato and coffee maker
put down container on the white table to the right of the tomato
anns.task_desc: pick up knife, put it in container on stove top, put the container on the white table next to tomato
